sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Owner Browser
  participant A as ASP.NET Core API
  participant D as Postgres

  U->>A: POST /api/orgs/{orgId}/billing/upgrade (Bearer JWT)
  A->>D: begin; set local role authenticated; set_config('app.user_id', sub, true)
  A->>D: select app.set_org_plan(orgId, 'pro')
  D->>D: verify app.can_manage_org(orgId)
  D->>D: update entitlements row
  D->>D: insert plan_changes audit row
  A->>D: commit
  A-->>U: 200 { plan: "pro", ... }
  U->>A: Refetch GET /api/orgs/{orgId}/billing and dashboard
  A-->>U: plan = pro, limits lifted, history shows audit row
